	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />You can tell it would be impossible just by looking at screens of the Metroid 23rd Anniversary hack.  There's a minimap in the corner overlaid over the rest of the game, as well as a timer and other things.  This might be possible to add to the game but it would take a huge overhaul, and your certainly couldn't just overlay it.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
